    "description": "Stabilize the new union_topk family with a complementary-proposal encoder: the linear path still anchors selection, but the nonlinear branch now reads the linear residual and can surface extra candidates that the baseline top-k misses. This is a single quality-first proxy follow-up on the most recent new family, rather than another local sweep on hybrid_topk.",
